{"tid":388760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗黃金數碼廣場將被出售，地庫改為惠康，地面變成餐飲，一樓做酒樓","createTime":"2017-09-05T16:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T17:00:56.000Z","uid":53922,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5515224258bb4b2dbd1eca1262539eb15c8c964","tid":388760,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1352513-20170905.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1352513-20170905.htm&d=xzt1sFAiRERj%2BDL7UucF8b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e51b3f8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1352513-20170905.htm&h=2989de16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1352513-20170905.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n高力國際獲業主委託，以遞交意向書形式出售黃金數碼廣場物業，下月20日中午截標。 <br />\n<br />\n黃金數碼廣場位於深水埗一線零售地段，門面面向福榮街及欽州街大單邊，步行至港鐵深水埗站約兩分鐘。物業總建築面積約24700平方呎，每層面積逾8000平方呎。地庫整層是超級市場，地下是特色餐飲及各式零售商店，一樓則為中式酒樓。<br />\n<br />\n高力國際預計，物業重新包裝及租客重整後每月總租金可達240萬元。"},{"pid":"aa0ade0ceb94b7feab69a9909f7f642c99dc97fc","tid":388760,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"一開始起除左樓上唔係食肆其他都差唔多"},{"pid":"d8aadd13b5891e3516c3dea21c170761a1b95c70","tid":388760,"uid":9777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"屌你，租貴無人嚟有撚用咩<br />\n做返電腦嘢好過啦"},{"pid":"0b9b8d6735870adb9d7e88a0592861136640fd2d","tid":388760,"uid":31031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"改到咁睇下你有幾多人流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beed1e9322560ce939f2d3759d5578c455d2351c","tid":388760,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"留名等睇新死場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ef14b465ee039a86aebe4f65043a3a5ee48d11","tid":388760,"uid":11280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"黃金數碼廣場 =/= 黃金電腦商場"},{"pid":"0595824453aa8945aba171765f73a4c3083dfe3c","tid":388760,"uid":3439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃金數碼廣場 =/= 黃金電腦商場</blockquote><br />\n步行至港鐵站兩分鐘<br />\n心諗妹極都唔駛兩分鐘啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee972699e2748f883a1f5b348b91e1e2a2be160e","tid":388760,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"搬去褔仁"}]}